Package: smack-utils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsmack (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Selection of tools for developers working with Smack.
 Tools provided to load and unload rules from the kernel and query the policy

